{"tid":1486182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831前必須要set死線逼政府回應","createTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T20:44:41.000Z","uid":251246,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a44a702f8852a7fd0cd9402bc9e5adec810996","tid":1486182,"uid":251246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政權 一拖再拖<br />\n五大訴求 刻不容緩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日，即使一百七十萬人出咗嚟和平示威，政府依然漠視民意。兩個月以來，有六位手足離開咗我哋、一位手足失去咗佢嘅眼睛、七百多人俾黑警拉咗、仲有無數嘅受傷者... 再拖落去，我哋只會有更多無辜嘅犧牲。因此，831示威前，我哋必須再set 死線逼政府回應。若然政府依然對訴求視若無暏，和理非同勇武就出師有名，喺831當日全面升級行動。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"4ad5ee5a3b639d4e90f77f7140b04387dcd43173","tid":1486182,"uid":251246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政權 一拖再拖<br />\n五大訴求 刻不容緩</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ddf10c05eec2b765af91c6ff49d168c9429acd2","tid":1486182,"uid":251246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:32:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政權 一拖再拖<br />\n五大訴求 刻不容緩</span></span>"},{"pid":"3eff334c05b06e45c1b166b9cc5ac29b3b8aab54","tid":1486182,"uid":251246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:33:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政權 一拖再拖<br />\n五大訴求 刻不容緩</span></span>"},{"pid":"a98a80dd2c52c9b1251403a2605a691701fb8ae1","tid":1486182,"uid":251246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:33:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政權 一拖再拖<br />\n五大訴求 刻不容緩</span></span>"},{"pid":"5e91dacd17a66f8df3e8d5c376352d8c1d7e3958","tid":1486182,"uid":251246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\